          "description": "Scenic drive through rolling tea hills and waterfalls to Ella. Walk to the famous Nine Arches Bridge – spot a train crossing through the jungle canopy. Hike Little Adam's Peak for breathtaking views. Afternoon: Flying Rawana Adventure Park (zip-lining, archery). Visit Rawana Cave Temple and Rawana Waterfall (Rawana Ella Falls)."
