          "description": "Drive south to Yala. Full day game drive in Yala National Park – home to the highest leopard density in the world. Spot Sri Lankan leopards, wild elephants, sloth bears, crocodiles, spotted deer, water buffalo, peacocks and hundreds of bird species."
        },
        {
          "day": "Day 7",
          "location": "Mirissa",
          "description": "Drive along the south coast to Mirissa. Pre-dawn whale watching boat – blue whales and sperm whales are frequently spotted off Mirissa. Explore Secret Beach (hidden cove). Visit Coconut Tree Hill (iconic photographic spot). Climb Parrot Rock for sweeping ocean views. You can also surf 🏄‍♀️ at Mirissa Beach."
        },
        {
          "day": "Day 8",
